nl.naturalis.nda.domain

Class NdaTraceableObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.naturalis.nda.domain.NdaDomainObject
      • nl.naturalis.nda.domain.NdaTraceableObject
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    MultiMediaObject, Specimen, Taxon

    public abstract class NdaTraceableObject
extends NdaDomainObject
    The base class for all domain objects within the NDA API that can be traced back to a single record in one of the NDA's source systems. In other words, these objects are not aggregations or assembled from multiple source systems.
